text: Gabbasovo () is a rural locality (a village) in Muynaksky Selsoviet, Zianchurinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 118 as of 2010. There is 1 street. == Geography == It is located 43 km from Isyangulovo, 15 km from Verkhny Muynak. == References == Category:Rural localities in Zianchurinsky District
title: Gabbasovo
